OL,3,CClub 'heartbroken' after footballer
OL,4,Cdies while waiting to play match
OL,6,FTeammates have paid tribute after a
OL,7,Fplayer suffered a cardiac arrest and
OL,8,Fdied while waiting to take part in a
OL,9,Fmatch.
OL,11,FRaman Sidhu was due to play for social
OL,12,Fmedia team Hashtag United's
OL,13,Finclusivity team on Saturday and was
OL,14,Fkicking a ball around with friends
OL,15,Fwhen he collapsed.
OL,17,FA spokesman for the club said
OL,18,Femergency services were called to
OL,19,FGarons Park in Southend and worked to
OL,20,Fsave the 22-year-old for more than two
OL,21,Fhours before he was declared dead.
