OL,6,FMatthew Napier posted on Instagram
OL,7,Fthat Mr Sidhu was "more than an
OL,8,Finclusive teammate" and had won the
OL,9,Fhearts of everyone he met "with his
OL,10,Fincredible dedication and commitment
OL,11,Fto the team".
OL,13,F"A true winner in every league and cup
OL,14,Fcompetition he played for," he added.
OL,15,F"We'll always look up and see his
OL,16,Fsmile in the sky; you've got the best
OL,17,Fseats up there to watch us play and
OL,18,Fwin for you."
