OL,6,FEllie Smith said her mother had been
OL,7,Fone of the people to try to revive Mr
OL,8,FSidhu at Garons Park.
OL,10,F"So sad that this happened to my team-
OL,11,Fmate, I will always remember him and
OL,12,Fmiss him so much," she said.
OL,14,FWriting on Instagram, Hashtag
OL,15,FInclusive United said: "Obviously this
OL,16,Fhas greatly affected us all and we
OL,17,Fwill continue to support all of our
OL,18,Fplayers and their families through
OL,19,Fthis terrible time.
