OL,6,F"Raman loved his football and he will
OL,7,Fbe greatly missed. He has left his
OL,8,Fmark on all of our hearts and we will
OL,9,Fensure that his memory will live on."
OL,11,FHashtag United was formed in 2016 by
OL,12,FYouTuber Spencer Owen who had built an
OL,13,Faudience online thanks to videos of
OL,14,Fhis friends playing friendlies around
OL,15,Fthe world.
OL,17,FThe club now runs multiple sides
OL,18,Fincluding a men's team playing in the
OL,19,FIsthmian League Premier, an FA Women's
OL,20,FNational League Southern Premier team,
OL,21,Fand more than 50 youth teams.
